Patcher Kernel Errors are usually the result of League not operating under the specific administrative privileges it requires. I recommend [configuring your system permissions](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204134104-Setting-up-your-Permissions) for League to ensure it can operate correctly.

Let me know if this resolved your issue.
